                <h2>Key Strategies for Your Success</h2>
                
                <div class="strategies-grid">
                    <!-- Strategy 1 -->
                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <div class="strategy-icon">📚</div>
                        <h3>Effective Study Strategies</h3>
                        <p>Maximize your learning efficiency and retention with proven study methods.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Actively recall information instead of passive re-reading.</li>
                            <li>Space out your study sessions over time (Spaced Repetition).</li>
                            <li>Interleave different subjects to improve problem-solving skills.</li>
                            <li>Use mind maps and visual aids to connect concepts.</li>
                            <li>Explain concepts to others to solidify your understanding.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Strategy 2 -->
                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <div class="strategy-icon">⏰</div>
                        <h3>Time Management & Organization</h3>
                        <p>Organize your academic and personal life for optimal productivity.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create a weekly study schedule and stick to it.</li>
                            <li>Break down large tasks into smaller, manageable steps.</li>
                            <li>Prioritize tasks using the Eisenhower Matrix (Urgent/Important).</li>
                            <li>Avoid multitasking; focus on one task at a time.</li>
                            <li>Schedule regular breaks to prevent burnout.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Strategy 3 -->
                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <div class="strategy-icon">👥</div>
                        <h3>Seeking Academic Support</h3>
                        <p>Leverage available resources to overcome challenges and excel.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Attend professor's office hours regularly for clarity and guidance.</li>
                            <li>Join study groups to collaborate and share insights.</li>
                            <li>Utilize campus tutoring services for challenging subjects.</li>
                            <li>Seek guidance from academic advisors for course planning.</li>
                            <li>Don't hesitate to ask questions in class or during discussions.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Strategy 4 -->
                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <div class="strategy-icon">❤️</div>
                        <h3>Well-being & Self-Care</h3>
                        <p>Maintain a healthy balance to sustain long-term academic success.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Get adequate sleep (7-9 hours) for optimal cognitive function.</li>
                            <li>Exercise regularly to reduce stress and improve focus.</li>
                            <li>Practice mindfulness or meditation for mental clarity.</li>
                            <li>Maintain a balanced diet to fuel your brain.</li>
                            <li>Build a support network of friends and family.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Strategy 5 -->
                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <div class="strategy-icon">📈</div>
                        <h3>Goal Setting & Motivation</h3>
                        <p>Set clear objectives and maintain momentum throughout your journey.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Set SMART goals (Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, Time-bound).</li>
                            <li>Track your progress and celebrate small wins.</li>
                            <li>Visualize your success and stay connected to your purpose.</li>
                            <li>Find an accountability partner or mentor.</li>
                            <li>Reflect regularly on your growth and learning.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Strategy 6 -->
                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <div class="strategy-icon">💡</div>
                        <h3>Financial Planning</h3>
                        <p>Manage your finances wisely to reduce stress and focus on studies.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create a realistic monthly budget and track expenses.</li>